name: sumi:(inked) #8 SPIDER
description:
🎃 halloween special 🎃
Spider, light orange Halloween macabre themed ink. 
These spiders can only be found on Halloween season, which makes them pretty exclusive, although they do come in high numbers each time. Particularly venomous so do be careful when handling. If you succeed to give her head a kiss without getting bit, you just might discover something...
